				<td colspan="2"><span>PoG was TEH cash machine for me for a LOOONG time.
<br />
Each mob dropped 1 high gem (diamond, BD, BS) or highend jewelery (ruby crown etc), sometimes the mob dropped both. Additionally you have a good chance for an armor piece you may want for alts and lots of spell drops including OOS.
<br />

<br />
Mobs were super easy and hitting like babies. They did summon, but who cares they are slowable and a slowed mob hitting for 100 ...<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />
Fear kiting worked too, if you really needed a break from melee.
<br />

<br />
This paradise which gave me approx 12 to 15 k in a 8 hour session is now closed for soloing since the PoGs are back. They aggro zonewide, no matter where u are, and its 3 of them. You still can hunt there with a small group for armor (if you havent better yet) and loads of cash.</span></td>
